<node id="Attachment J-0200000-17">
  <data key="d0">Attachment J-0200000-17</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment J-0200000-17 is an Excel spreadsheet containing worksheets for ELINs corresponding to each CLIN, used for pricing recurring and non-recurring work.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment J-0200000-17 contains worksheets with exhibit line item numbers and sub-ELINs for pricing various option periods and is referenced across multiple line items with instructions to use the most current version and check amendments.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment J-0200000-17 is the Exhibit Line Item Numbers attachment used for pricing spreadsheet data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759836281</data>
</node>
<node id="Water Annex">
  <data key="d0">Water Annex</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Water Annex specifies recurring Base Operations Support services for water-related requirements in the base period and option periods.&lt;SEP&gt;Water Annex is a specific area requiring recurring base operations support services as detailed in designated exhibit line items across option periods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759836281</data>
</node>
<node id="Port Operations">
  <data key="d0">Port Operations</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Port Operations is a required service under Base Operations Support at the specified locations.&lt;SEP&gt;Port Operations (0600000) is a technical annex requiring demonstration of relevant experience similar to RFP requirements for base operations support.&lt;SEP&gt;Port Operations is Annex 0600000, part of the scope for relevant Base Operations Support projects similar to RFP requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759836281</data>
