<node id="Facility Management">
  <data key="d0">Facility Management</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Facility Management is a required service under Base Operations Support at the specified locations.&lt;SEP&gt;Facility Management (1501000) is a sub-annex under Facilities Support, with two versions for NAVSTA and MCSF-BI, requiring performance methodology.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
