  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Integrated Solid Waste Management is a required service primarily at Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island.&lt;SEP&gt;Integrated Solid Waste Management (1503030) is a sub-annex for MCSF-BI under Facilities Support.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759836281</data>
