<node id="Utilities Management">
  <data key="d0">Utilities Management</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Utilities Management is a required service under Base Operations Support, including electrical, wastewater, steam, and water.&lt;SEP&gt;Utilities Management (1601000) is a sub-annex under Utilities in Annex 16, part of the performance methodology requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
