  <data key="d0">Standard Form 33</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Standard Form 33 is the prescribed form for the solicitation, offer, and award, revised in June 2014, used for sealed bid or negotiated contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;Standard Form 33 is a form to be completed and signed with UEI number and CAGE code for the offeror.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
