  <data key="d0">Custodial</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Custodial services are required under Base Operations Support, primarily performed at Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island.&lt;SEP&gt;Custodial (1503010) is a sub-annex for MCSF-BI under Facilities Support, included in technical approach requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Custodial services and maps are provided for MCSF-BI.</data>
