  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the contract solicitation document that includes sections on inspection, acceptance, and deliveries.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the procurement document for Mayport BOS, including various clauses and instructions.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the contract solicitation number associated with all clauses, sections, and attachments listed.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the procurement solicitation document containing annexes, sub-annexes, performance work statement, and evaluation factors for the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the contract solicitation number referenced throughout the document.</data>
