  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment JL-1 is a Microsoft Excel version required for basis of estimate on staffing levels for the total effort including prime and subcontractors.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment JL-1 is a spreadsheet detailing staffing levels and labor hours for the base period, including prime contractor and subcontractors.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment JL-1 is submitted as part of the non-price proposal requirements in hard copy and electronic format.</data>
