  <data key="d0">NAVSTA Mayport</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">NAVSTA Mayport is a naval station that distributes its own electricity and produces and distributes its own water, requiring adequate and sufficient utilities at all times.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVSTA Mayport is a naval station that distributes its own electricity and produces and distributes its own water, requiring continuous utility adequacy.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVSTA Mayport is referenced in facility inventories, site maps, historical work orders, and specific programs like Cross Connection Control.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455</data>
