  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">MCSF-BI is a facility site with specific sub-annexes for services like facility management, custodial, pest control, solid waste management, grounds maintenance, and environmental support.&lt;SEP&gt;MCSF-BI is associated with specific sub-annexes in Facilities Support and Environmental, requiring relevant experience demonstrations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCSF-BI is referenced in site visit itineraries, facility inventories, investments, and specific systems like auxiliary generators and lighting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455</data>
