  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The RFP is the solicitation document requiring proposals for base operations support services.&lt;SEP&gt;The RFP is the solicitation document outlining requirements, performance work statement, specifications, and evaluation factors for base operations support services.</data>
