  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Small Business represents a category targeted at 40% of total planned subcontract dollars in NAVFAC's subcontracting goals.&lt;SEP&gt;Small Business is a category with a 40% subcontracting target in NAVFAC's command-wide goals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
