  <data key="d2">Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business is a category targeted at 5% of total planned subcontract dollars in NAVFAC's subcontracting goals.&lt;SEP&gt;Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business is a category with a 5% subcontracting target in NAVFAC's command-wide goals.&lt;SEP&gt;Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business is a set-aside category for contracts performed in the United States or outlying areas.</data>
