  <data key="d0">Systems Approach</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Systems Approach involves maintaining systems without listing every ancillary part but including all mechanically and electrically interlocked parts, equipment, and components to form functioning systems like fire protection, HVAC, and utility systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759836290</data>
