<edge source="Government" target="Contractor">
  <data key="d6">2.0</data>
  <data key="d7">The Government contracts with the Contractor for services, estimating costs and imposing liquidated damages for nonperformance.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government inspects and assesses the Contractor's performance in accordance with FAR 52.246-4.</data>
  <data key="d8">contractual obligation,inspection,performance,performance requirements</data>
  <data key="d9">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1</data>
