  <data key="d11">1759836303</data>
</edge>
<edge source="Government" target="Option to Extend Services">
  <data key="d6">1.0</data>
  <data key="d7">Government may exercise the Option to Extend Services clause to require continued performance from the Contractor.</data>
  <data key="d8">extension authority,service continuation</data>
  <data key="d9">chunk-bafeb026eba657c5147474a89dc0e6f9</data>
  <data key="d10">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d11">1759836305</data>
</edge>
<edge source="Government" target="Option to Extend the Term of the Contract">
  <data key="d6">1.0</data>
  <data key="d7">Government can extend the contract term using the Option to Extend the Term of the Contract clause via written notice.</data>
  <data key="d8">notice requirement,term extension</data>
