</edge>
<edge source="Facilities Support Services" target="Small Business Size Standard">
  <data key="d6">1.0</data>
  <data key="d7">Facilities support services under NAICS 561210 have a small business size standard of $47,000,000.</data>
  <data key="d8">eligibility requirement,size determination</data>
