<edge source="52.204-5 Women-Owned Business Other Than Small Business" target="Simplified Acquisition Threshold">
  <data key="d6">1.0</data>
  <data key="d7">Simplified Acquisition Threshold determines applicability of 52.204-5 for non-set-aside solicitations exceeding the threshold.</data>
